reviews.review_text: - I think this treatment has made the sound way more tinny and hard to listen to than the original Wise recording. All the warmth is gone. Sorry Charlie. And I'm not trying to be a smartass with the "sorry Charlie".

What???? came here to grab one day after 9/13 and am stunned at this guys opinion below. Dude you are DEAF. This version has more clarity and oomph to say the least. Seriously it is way better than the old version. Get the weed resin out of your ears cuz they are blocked up real bad!
